600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Among-Us-VR-_-ティザートレイラー-_-Meta-Quest-Rift-0-7-screenshot.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1096768" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Among-Us-VR-_-ティザートレイラー-_-Meta-Quest-Rift-0-7-screenshot-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Among-Us-VR-_-ティザートレイラー-_-Meta-Quest-Rift-0-7-screenshot-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Among-Us-VR-_-ティザートレイラー-_-Meta-Quest-Rift-0-7-screenshot-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Among-Us-VR-_-ティザートレイラー-_-Meta-Quest-Rift-0-7-screenshot-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Among-Us-VR-_-ティザートレイラー-_-Meta-Quest-Rift-0-7-screenshot-1536x864.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Among-Us-VR-_-ティザートレイラー-_-Meta-Quest-Rift-0-7-screenshot.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>第一人稱視點將帶來更強烈的現場感。在廠方發佈的影片中可看到，玩家在遊戲中變成了半「動作」遊戲，無論是兇手要殺人，或者明知某人是兇手而要逃跑，都是直接操作角色。而場景的太空空間也是 3D 表示。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Among-Us-VR-_-ティザートレイラー-_-Meta-Quest-Rift-0-27-screenshot.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1096763" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Among-Us-VR-_-ティザートレイラー-_-Meta-Quest-Rift-0-27-screenshot-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Among-Us-VR-_-ティザートレイラー-_-Meta-Quest-Rift-0-27-screenshot-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Among-Us-VR-_-ティザートレイラー-_-Meta-Quest-Rift-0-27-screenshot-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Among-Us-VR-_-ティザートレイラー-_-Meta-Quest-Rift-0-27-screenshot-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Among-Us-VR-_-ティザートレイラー-_-Meta-Quest-Rift-0-27-screenshot-1536x864.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Among-Us-VR-_-ティザートレイラー-_-Meta-Quest-Rift-0-27-screenshot.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>《Among Us》多人遊戲中，其中一至數名玩家會秘密變成殺人兇手，在遊戲中刺害其他玩家；而每過一個回合，所有玩家都會展開會議，兇手與一般玩家會一齊討論誰是兇手，所有玩家會鬥智鬥力務求找出／不被其他人發現自己是兇手。</p><p><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_89446"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/wzYw5FWsdwI?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wzYw5FWsdwI"> YouTube</a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
